1171
01:17:43,113 --> 01:17:48,483
[Breeze gusts]

1172
01:17:53,123 --> 01:17:54,454
[E-mail alert sounds]

1173
01:18:07,270 --> 01:18:09,534
[Motion detector alerts snap on]

1174
